                If that is not an option, the best way to reach me is via on LinkedIn.
                {# <a href="mailto:andreas@example.com" class="link-blue">Email</a>. #}
            </p>
            
            <div class="contact-icons">
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/andreas-jaramillo" class="icon-circle">
                    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/linkedin.png" alt="LinkedIn">
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/andyjaramillo" class="icon-circle">
                    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/github--v1.png" alt="GitHub">
                </a>
            </div>
            <small class="attribution">Icons by <a href="https://icons8.com">icons8.com</a></small>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-image">
            <img src="/assets/profile.jpg" alt="Andreas Jaramillo" class="round-profile">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>